{"tid":2265183,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何猷君爆大學時立志要娶奚夢瑤 網民質疑過去情史為追老婆攞經驗","createTime":"2020-10-31T08:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T11:12:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"21b403e6c5baa20b4186eb2eedbf8068a172d4c8","tid":2265183,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T08:22:39.000Z","msg":"賭王四房兒子何猷君近日孖老婆奚夢瑤參加中國真人騷《幸福三重奏》，他不時在節目中放閃，他更自爆如何抱得美人歸，何猷君謂中學時便喜歡奚夢瑤，他讀大學時便立志要娶奚夢瑤為妻，但追求過程漫長，他說：「約她晚飯一直不肯。」奚夢瑤卻整蠱說吃飯要中午，她更爆料指以前對何猷君印象是「花心」，他花了不少脣舌和行動為自己澄清。他認真解說長得帥不能等於花心，最終真誠奪得芳心，二人拍拖時，他甚至包下一間戲院邀請女友看戲。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201031/WFKYBMAXTRCJ5MPLYEKMYL5APU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201031%2FWFKYBMAXTRCJ5MPLYEKMYL5APU%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak8%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=8a8bd43e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201031%2FWFKYBMAXTRCJ5MPLYEKMYL5APU%2F&h=a64fffa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201031/WFKYBMAXTRCJ5MPLYEKMYL5APU/</a>"},{"pid":"37fb826442065a3aff1adce643fefb730291286d","tid":2265183,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:48:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b36d066e6046495ceae96af7732e531e3bb7d352","tid":2265183,"uid":165136,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:11:20.000Z","msg":"他認真解說長得帥不能等於花心<br />\n<br />\n但人地覺得你花心應該唔係呢個原因"},{"pid":"fced4cec683cee90d8e753e5a6061377eea5ac66","tid":2265183,"uid":54930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:11:57.000Z","msg":"關我地撚事咩"},{"pid":"bb0760fca8ae6180d62a71a38c3fff3034e920e3","tid":2265183,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b36d066e6046495ceae96af7732e531e3bb7d352","tid":2265183,"uid":165136,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:11:20.000Z","msg":"他認真解說長得帥不能等於花